@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
    Layout = "../Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}
<div class="w-50 m-auto">

    <h2 class="heading mb-5 fw-bolder mt-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h2>

    <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> January 1, 2024</p>
    <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> March 10, 2024</p>

    <p>Welcome to <strong>Task Management</strong>. Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, share, and safeguard your information when you use our App.</p>

    <h4 class="fw-bold">1. Information We Collect</h4>
    <h5>1.1 Personal Information</h5>
    <ul>
        <li>Name</li>
        <li>Email address</li>
        <li>Contact details</li>
    </ul>

    <h5>1.2 Task Data</h5>
    <ul>
        <li>Tasks you create, assign, or complete</li>
        <li>Deadlines, descriptions, and other details related to your tasks</li>
    </ul>

    <h5>1.3 Device and Usage Information</h5>
    <ul>
        <li>IP address</li>
        <li>Browser type and version</li>
        <li>Operating system</li>
        <li>Usage statistics, such as login time and features used</li>
    </ul>

    <h5>1.4 Cookies</h5>
    <p>We use cookies to enhance your experience, save your preferences, and provide analytics about App usage.</p>

    <h4 class="fw-bold">2. How We Use Your Information</h4>
    <p>We use the information collected for the following purposes:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>To provide, operate, and maintain the App</li>
        <li>To manage your account and task data</li>
        <li>To communicate with you, including sending notifications about task updates</li>
        <li>To personalize your experience</li>
        <li>To improve our services and implement new features</li>
        <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
    </ul>

    <h4 class="fw-bold">3. Sharing Your Information</h4>
    <p>We do not sell your information to third parties. However, we may share your information with:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> For hosting, analytics, and payment processing</li>
        <li><strong>Business Transfers:</strong> In case of a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets</li>
        <li><strong>Legal Compliance:</strong> To comply with applicable laws, regulations, or legal processes</li>
    </ul>

    <h4 class="fw-bold">4. Security of Your Information</h4>
    <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to secure your personal data. However, no method of transmission over the Internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure. Therefore, we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

    <h4 class="fw-bold">5. Your Rights</h4>
    <p>You have the following rights regarding your personal data:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Access, correct, or delete your personal information</li>
        <li>Opt-out of certain data processing activities</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
        <li>Lodge a complaint with a data protection authority if you believe your rights are being violated</li>
    </ul>
    <p>To exercise your rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@taskflowmanager.com">support@taskflowmanager.com</a>.</p>

    <h4 class="fw-bold">6. Data Retention</h4>
    <p>We retain your information as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy or comply with legal obligations. Once your data is no longer required, we will delete or anonymize it.</p>

    <h4 class="fw-bold">7. Third-Party Links</h4>
    <p>Our App may contain links to third-party websites or services. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third parties. Please review their privacy policies before providing any personal data.</p>

    <h4 class="fw-bold">8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h4>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date. We encourage you to review this page periodically.</p>

    <h4 class="fw-bold">9. Contact Us</h4>
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our practices, please contact us at:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@taskflowmanager.com">support@taskflowmanager.com</a></li>
        <li><strong>Phone:</strong> +1-555-123-4567</li>
        <li><strong>Address:</strong> 123 TaskFlow Lane, Productivity City, PC 56789</li>
    </ul>

    <p>This Privacy Policy is governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the United States.</p>
</div>